pirate-recruitment-contract-content = { "[head=2]PIRATE ARTICLES[/head]" }

    The undersigned willingly renounces NanoTrasen law and joins the pirate crew.

    { "[bold]The undersigned agrees to:[/bold]" }
    • obey the captain until they prove themselves a landlubber;
    • refrain from stealing from the crew without a truly compelling reason;
    • share the loot after the captain's cut;
    • never abandon a crewmate while a ransom can still be collected.

    { "[bold]The crew agrees to:[/bold]" }
    • treat the undersigned as one of their own;
    • provide a share of the loot, a bunk, and a vote during any mutiny.

    { "[italic]Make your mark, and from this day your home lies beneath the Jolly Roger.[/italic]" }
